title: 12/17/12 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 12/17/12 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses last night's Chiefs/Chargers game. How will Covid affect this weekend's games. Brady Quinn calls in to discuss why the Chargers went for it multiple times last night instead of taking the points. And Mike Florio explains why Deshaun Watson is still in Houston.
